name: Migration
description:
"Migration" is a piece of digital collage that comes from my first zine book.
Leaving your home.
Leaving your family.
Leaving your memories.
Leaving your love.
ALL eyes are on you and you have to shine like a diamond in your way.
One hand picks you up and takes you to another location, and you have to continue your way.
Where are you?
Are you in your correct location?
